### Eureka Server API Test File

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:8761/actuator/health

### Eureka Dashboard (Basic Auth required)
# Use browser: http://localhost:8761
# Username: admin
# Password: password

### Get Applications Registry
GET http://admin:password@localhost:8761/eureka/apps

### Get specific service status
GET http://admin:password@localhost:8761/eureka/apps/eureka-server
